title: Car crashes at Volcom mini ramp contest at ISPO tradeshow
description: During the Knot Again mini ramp practice, a car crashed onto the ramp. But the fun still continues, today, 30 January, 14:00 the contest will run, be sure to stop by the Volcom booth at ISPO to watch the action. Caution of crashing cars!
